<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 18:09:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着拜登再次拯救以色列，其无能领导人为特朗普竞选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-04/ty-article/.highlight/as-biden-comes-to-israels-rescue-again-its-inept-leaders-campaign-for-trump/00000191-1e26-d5b2-afb7-de7ef1ed0000</link><description>以色列不一定要接受美国的每一项要求，对华盛顿的每一项政策建议都说“是”，但至少，其无能的领导层——导致1200多名以色列人死亡、这是该国历史上最大的失败——应该承担责任。谦虚一点</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 17:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-04/ty-article/.highlight/as-biden-comes-to-israels-rescue-again-its-inept-leaders-campaign-for-trump/00000191-1e26-d5b2-afb7-de7ef1ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 303 天：加沙记录的乙型肝炎病例超过 10 万例</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-303-over-100-000-cases-of-hepatitis-b-recorded-in-gaza/00000191-1e43-d68e-a79b-5fd7a4f20001</link><description>两名以色列人在霍隆市的刺伤袭击中丧生，两人中度受伤 ■ 美国高级官员告诉《国土报》，拜登已经意识到内塔尼亚胡在寻求人质释放协议方面向他撒谎 ■ 大特拉维夫地区居民报告 GPS 严重中断 ■ 据报道，伊朗告诉阿拉伯国家外交官们，它不在乎对哈尼亚被杀的反应是否会引发地区战争 ■ 战争已经过去 303 天了，你需要知道的就是这些</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 17:43:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-303-over-100-000-cases-of-hepatitis-b-recorded-in-gaza/00000191-1e43-d68e-a79b-5fd7a4f20001</guid></item><item><title>以色列和真主党的“火战”：卫星图像揭示了毁灭性的破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollah-and-israels-war-of-fire-satellite-images-reveal-its-devastating-effect/00000191-1dbf-db97-a7df-fdff6c4e0000</link><description>图片显示，自敌对行动爆发以来 — — 但主要是自 5 月以来 — — 以色列和黎巴嫩约有 210,000 德南被烧毁。以色列的烧焦总面积是以色列历史上两场最大火灾烧毁面积的三倍</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 16:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/hezbollah-and-israels-war-of-fire-satellite-images-reveal-its-devastating-effect/00000191-1dbf-db97-a7df-fdff6c4e0000</guid></item><item><title>由于两国关系紧张，以色列外交部长用土耳其语抨击埃尔多安后走红</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-goes-viral-after-blasting-erdogan-in-turkish-as-ties-between-countries-strain/00000191-1d55-d534-a9f9-7d5ddfa60000</link><description>以色列外交部长严厉斥责埃尔多安，称土耳其总统支持“杀人犯和强奸犯”，正在“摧毁”土耳其，而以色列和土耳其关系因加沙战争而持续恶化</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:40:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-goes-viral-after-blasting-erdogan-in-turkish-as-ties-between-countries-strain/00000191-1d55-d534-a9f9-7d5ddfa60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前部长的儿子于 10 月 7 日被杀，成为支持内塔尼亚胡的网络仇恨目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/ex-minister-whose-son-was-killed-on-oct-7-targeted-by-pro-netanyahu-online-hate/00000191-1ddb-d1c6-a591-9ddfe8eb0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡前部长伊扎尔·谢伊在因批评以色列政策而受到内塔尼亚胡支持者的辱骂后表示，“我们将与那些心怀恶意的人作斗争，他们瞄准死者家属的家长，希望我和我的孩子都死掉”。下午</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 15:31:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/ex-minister-whose-son-was-killed-on-oct-7-targeted-by-pro-netanyahu-online-hate/00000191-1ddb-d1c6-a591-9ddfe8eb0000</guid></item><item><title>贝都因青少年在攀爬基布兹围栏后被枪杀。他的父亲正在寻求正义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bedouin-teen-was-shot-dead-after-climbing-a-kibbutzs-fence-his-fathers-seeking-justice/00000191-1d00-d534-a9f9-7d0912850000</link><description>一名 18 岁少年被南部基布兹保安队一名涉嫌盗窃的成员杀害。这位年轻人的父亲希望能够告诉他的孩子们，以色列仍然是一个法治国家</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 13:09:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bedouin-teen-was-shot-dead-after-climbing-a-kibbutzs-fence-his-fathers-seeking-justice/00000191-1d00-d534-a9f9-7d0912850000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫和以色列中部报告 GPS 干扰，与 4 月伊朗袭击前夕相呼应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/gps-jamming-reported-in-tel-aviv-and-central-israel-echoing-eve-of-aprils-iran-attack/00000191-1d01-d534-a9f9-7d09a4400000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，GPS 中断在以色列北部已司空见惯，但在特拉维夫却很少见。以色列国防军此前承认，卫星干扰是针对 GPS 制导无人机或导弹的主动措施</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 12:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/gps-jamming-reported-in-tel-aviv-and-central-israel-echoing-eve-of-aprils-iran-attack/00000191-1d01-d534-a9f9-7d09a4400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军起诉延长了对涉嫌虐待斯德·泰曼的五名以色列士兵的拘留期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/prosecution-seeks-extended-custody-of-five-israeli-soldiers-suspected-of-sde-teiman-abuse/00000191-1caf-db97-a7df-fcffecc00000</link><description>以色列国防军法院审查了延长八名嫌疑人还押候审的请求，这些嫌疑人被指控在被俘恐怖分子拘留中心严重虐待一名加沙被拘留者。在听证会上，检方表示，针对五名嫌疑人的证据已得到显着加强</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 12:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/prosecution-seeks-extended-custody-of-five-israeli-soldiers-suspected-of-sde-teiman-abuse/00000191-1caf-db97-a7df-fcffecc00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在巴黎奥运会上取得空前成功的秘诀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/the-secret-to-israels-success-at-the-paris-olympics/00000191-1d00-da43-afdf-3f229bc00000</link><description>多年的投资让人们对以色列在 2024 年奥运会上抱有很高的期望，但这些期望在神奇的三天里被超越了，以色列获得了六枚奥运会奖牌，其中包括一枚金牌。团队是这样做的</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 11:29:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/the-secret-to-israels-success-at-the-paris-olympics/00000191-1d00-da43-afdf-3f229bc00000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫郊区发生刺伤袭击，两名以色列人死亡，两人受伤；恐怖分子被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-killed-two-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-suspect-shot-dead/00000191-1c49-d803-afb9-bc4b95b80000</link><description>一名66岁妇女当场被宣告死亡，一名80多岁男子在医院伤重不治身亡；以色列警方称袭击者是来自约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 10:04:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/two-israelis-killed-two-wounded-in-stabbing-attack-suspect-shot-dead/00000191-1c49-d803-afb9-bc4b95b80000</guid></item><item><title>绝望的加沙人向 GoFundMe 寻求帮助。它并不总是有回报</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/desperate-gazans-turned-to-gofundme-for-help-it-didnt-always-pay-off/00000191-08ff-dc1a-a1b7-19ff56ee0000</link><description>数以万计的巴勒斯坦人利用众筹网站筹集了重要资金，以帮助他们生存或逃离加沙地带。但有些人面临着剥削、繁文缛节、限制和延误，这可能是生死攸关的问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 08:43:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/desperate-gazans-turned-to-gofundme-for-help-it-didnt-always-pay-off/00000191-08ff-dc1a-a1b7-19ff56ee0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗不顾克制呼吁，内塔尼亚胡将召集安全负责人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-live/idf-about-30-rockets-fired-in-barrage-on-north-combat-soldier-seriously-wounded-in-gaza/00000191-1b5b-dd06-a3f7-9b5f2cc50000</link><description>美国将军周一将在伊朗预计发动袭击之前访问以色列 ■ 以色列国防军在计划行动之前下令撤离汗尤尼斯南部和拉法北部地区 ■ 巴勒斯坦报告称，以色列对加沙两所学校的袭击至少造成 25 人死亡；以色列国防军称其目标是藏匿在那里的哈马斯特工 ■ 也门胡塞武装称他们用弹道导弹瞄准了亚丁湾的船只</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 03:58:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article-live/idf-about-30-rockets-fired-in-barrage-on-north-combat-soldier-seriously-wounded-in-gaza/00000191-1b5b-dd06-a3f7-9b5f2cc50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备反击伊朗，内塔尼亚胡却让公众蒙在鼓里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-for-irans-counterattack-netanyahu-leaves-the-public-in-the-dark/00000191-19ae-db97-a7df-fdfee73e0000</link><description>与四月份不同的是，德黑兰对以色列遭受的袭击保持无线电沉默。与此同时，政府已免于向公民解释会发生什么，而总理正忙于推翻以色列国防部长的运动</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 03:02:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-04/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-for-irans-counterattack-netanyahu-leaves-the-public-in-the-dark/00000191-19ae-db97-a7df-fdfee73e0000</guid></item><item><title>美国官员：拜登意识到内塔尼亚胡在人质交易上向他撒谎</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-biden-realized-netanyahu-lied-to-him-about-hostage-deal/00000191-19c0-d051-a3f7-d9cc68ce0000</link><description>拜登政府一名高级官员告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡对美国“忘恩负义”，并指出总理和拜登之间的过去两次对话既艰难又紧张</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 20:32:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/u-s-official-biden-realized-netanyahu-lied-to-him-about-hostage-deal/00000191-19c0-d051-a3f7-d9cc68ce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列全国各地抗议，人质家属称内塔尼亚胡选择升级而不是达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pm-chose-escalation-over-deal/00000191-18f8-d116-a9db-dcfda6d00000</link><description>人质亲属发誓不会放弃要求达成人质协议的示威活动，而通常每周举行的反政府抗议活动因担心伊朗或其代理人发动袭击而被取消</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:42:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pm-chose-escalation-over-deal/00000191-18f8-d116-a9db-dcfda6d00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第302天：人质家属称内塔尼亚胡选择升级而不是达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-302-mossad-shin-bet-chief-travel-to-egypt-and-return/00000191-1913-db97-a7df-fdfb8d3f0000</link><description>以色列谈判小组高级成员告诉《国土报》，以色列国防部长认为总理内塔尼亚胡对释放人质/停火协议不感兴趣 ■ 据报道，瑞典关闭了驻贝鲁特的贝鲁特大使馆，美国、英国敦促黎巴嫩国民尽快离开该国■ 以色列摩萨德和辛贝特领导人前往埃及并返回以色列继续停战谈判 ■ 战争开始 302 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-302-mossad-shin-bet-chief-travel-to-egypt-and-return/00000191-1913-db97-a7df-fdfb8d3f0000</guid></item><item><title>由于地区紧张局势和价格飙升，这些航空公司削减了飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-airlines-cutting-flights-to-israel-as-regional-tensions-and-prices-skyrocket/00000191-1457-db7e-a99d-1edf0f6b0000</link><description>到目前为止，所有为以色列服务的美国航空公司以及几家欧洲航空公司都已暂停航班。以色列旗舰航空公司以色列航空维持正常航班，但票价却飙升</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 16:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/these-are-the-airlines-cutting-flights-to-israel-as-regional-tensions-and-prices-skyrocket/00000191-1457-db7e-a99d-1edf0f6b0000</guid></item><item><title>官员警告称，恐怖组织利用阿拉伯犯罪组织袭击以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/arab-crime-organizations-being-used-by-terror-groups-to-attack-israel-officials-warn/00000191-18ad-d4cf-afb5-5cfdf97d0000</link><description>以色列国防官员警告部长们，“有组织犯罪对国家安全构成战略威胁”，并警告外国恐怖组织已经试图利用以色列境内的犯罪组织实施袭击。</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 15:39:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/arab-crime-organizations-being-used-by-terror-groups-to-attack-israel-officials-warn/00000191-18ad-d4cf-afb5-5cfdf97d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人阿尔乔姆·多尔戈皮亚特在巴黎奥运会体操自由体操决赛中获得银牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-gymnast-artem-dolgopyat-clinches-silver-medal-at-paris-olympics-gymnastics-final/00000191-188d-dd1b-a9f5-ff8d36ec0000</link><description>多尔戈皮亚特的胜利使以色列的奥运奖牌总数达到 19 枚，其中 6 枚是在 2024 年巴黎奥运会上获得的</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 14:27:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-gymnast-artem-dolgopyat-clinches-silver-medal-at-paris-olympics-gymnastics-final/00000191-188d-dd1b-a9f5-ff8d36ec0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列人质埃坦·利维 (Eitan Levy) 的家人公布了加沙人踢打、虐待他身体的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-hostage-eitan-levy-release-footage-of-gazans-abusing-his-body-on-oct-7/00000191-186a-d053-a7ff-5bfee3bd0000</link><description>利维于 10 月 7 日被杀，他的尸体被运往加沙。视频显示，利维的尸体在一辆汽车的敞开的后备箱中，后来躺在地上，而加沙人则对其进行拳打脚踢。 Levy是一名53岁的出租车司机，10月7日在载着一名乘客前往加沙边境时被杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 03 Aug 2024 14:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-israeli-hostage-eitan-levy-release-footage-of-gazans-abusing-his-body-on-oct-7/00000191-186a-d053-a7ff-5bfee3bd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>